- 0.0.4

- refactoring code to make it more readble

- 0.0.3

- recurse_pwdrc() has been added in the set of definable functions, it is
  called each time the user walks into a sub-directory

- todo_remider cookbook improved. It doesn't conflict anymore if used in
  multiple directories and it support the shuffle of the output

- 0.0.2

- New cookbooks:
  automount, cvsroot, gqview_imgdir, ls_alias, newmail_mutt_Z, todo_reminder
  
- Fixed a nasty bug which didn't allow to `cd' in directories whose name had a
  spaces or special chars.

- 0.0.1

- First release
